claim.claim-text:
1. A suspension apparatus for a hollow railway sleeper housing rail wheel undercarriage sensing equipment, the suspension apparatus comprising:
a cover attachment portion attached to a cover enclosing an equipment suspension cavity;
an equipment carrier attachment portion attached to an equipment carrier;
a deformable element disposed between the cover attachment portion and the equipment carrier attachment portion; and
a limiting member limiting deformation of the deformable element, wherein the limiting member includes a tubular member having a “C” shaped cross section longitudinally disposed partially around the exterior of the deformable element.

8. A system for suspending rail wheel undercarriage+temperature sensing equipment within a hollow railway sleeper, the system comprising:
an equipment carrier disposed within an equipment suspension cavity;
temperature sensing system components mounted to the equipment carrier;
a suspension apparatus configured to suspend the equipment carrier in the equipment suspension cavity, the suspension apparatus including:
a cover attachment portion attached to an equipment suspension cavity cover;
an equipment carrier attachment portion attached to the equipment carrier;
a deformable element disposed between the cover attachment portion and the equipment carrier attachment portion; and
a limiting member surrounding a majority of the deformable element and limiting deformation of the deformable element, wherein the limiting member includes a tubular member having a “C” shaped cross section longitudinally disposed partially around the exterior of the deformable element.

16. A hollow railway sleeper housing rail wheel undercarriage temperature sensing equipment, the railway sleeper comprising:
a shell defining an equipment suspension cavity;
a cover enclosing the equipment suspension cavity;
an equipment carrier disposed within the equipment suspension cavity;
temperature sending system components mounted to the equipment carrier;
a suspension apparatus configured to suspend the equipment carrier in the equipment suspension cavity, the suspension apparatus including:
a cover attachment portion attached to the cover;
an equipment carrier attachment portion attached to the equipment carrier;
a deformable element disposed between the cover attachment portion and the equipment carrier attachment portion; and
a limiting member limiting deformation of the deformable element, wherein the limiting member includes a tubular member having a “C” shaped cross section longitudinally disposed partially around the exterior of the deformable element.
